#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1202
msgid "Ingress with MetalLB"
msgstr "IngressとMetalLB"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1203
msgid ""
"As Traefik is already serving as an ingress controller, we can expose any "
"HTTP/HTTPS traffic via an <literal>Ingress</literal> object such as:"
