#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1625
msgid ""
"This section covers how to migrate your <literal>Edge 3.0.X</literal> "
"downstream clusters to <literal>Edge 3.1.0</literal>."
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、<literal>Edge 3.0.X</"
"literal>ダウンストリームクラスタを<literal>Edge 3.1."
