"ストのバックアップを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1642
msgid ""
"The backup location can be changed by defining the <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/blob/release-3.1.0/fleets/day2/system-"
"upgrade-controller-plans/eib-charts-migration-prep/plan."
"yaml#L36\"><literal>MANIFEST_BACKUP_DIR</literal></link> environment "
