#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1656
msgid ""
"This section describes how to convert the <literal>eib-chart-migration-prep</"
"literal> Fleet to a <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-"
"add\">Bundle</link> resource that can then be used in air-gapped "
"environments that cannot utilize a local git server."
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、<literal>eib-chart-migration-prep</literal> "
