"os-upgrade/os-upgrade-bundle.yaml\">バンドルコンテンツ</link>を<literal>suse-"
"edge/fleet-examples</literal>から<emphasis role=\"strong\">［Create from "
"YAML (YAMLから作成)］</emphasis>ページに手動でコピーする。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1847
msgid ""
