#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2096
msgid ""
"Convert the <literal>Longhorn CRD</literal> Helm chart Fleet to a Bundle "
"resource. For more information, see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/"
"bundle-add#convert-a-helm-chart-into-a-bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a "
