"<literal>longhorn-bundle.yaml</literal>と<literal>longhorn-crd-bundle."
"yaml</literal>を<literal>管理クラスタ</literal>にデプロイします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2098
msgid ""
"Following these steps will ensure that <literal>Longhorn</literal> is "
"deployed on all of the specified target clusters."
